parametersDescriptions.defaultOpen: If true, the menu will be initially open.
parametersDescriptions.onOpenChange: Callback fired when the menu is opened or closed.
parametersDescriptions.open: If true, the menu will be open. This is the controlled equivalent of the defaultOpen parameter.

returnValueDescriptions.contextValue: The value to be passed into the MenuProvider.
returnValueDescriptions.dispatch:
Action dispatcher for the menu component.
Allows to programmatically control the menu.
returnValueDescriptions.getListboxProps: Resolver for the listbox component's props.
returnValueDescriptions.highlightedValue: The highlighted option in the menu listbox.
